### 1. Регистрация нового человека (создание)
POST http://localhost:8092/v1/persons
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Иван",
  "lastName": "Петров",
  "email": "ivan.petrov@example.com",
  "passport_number": "1234 567890",
  "phone_number": "+79161234567",
  "address": {
    "address": "ул. Ленина, д. 15, кв. 42",
    "zip_code": "101000",
    "city": "Москва",
    "country_code": "RUS"
  }
}

